Student Robotics 2015 under way with new kit
===========================================
<img class="right" src="/images/content/news/sr2015/srteams.png" width="400" height="800" alt="Location of UK based teams entering Student Robotics 2015">

The 2015 Student Robotics competition has started with various [Kickstart](/events/kickstart) events.
Three Kickstarts were held at the University of Southampton, the University of Bristol and Facebook HQ in London.
There is also a Kickstart event occuring in Munich slightly later in the year.

There will be 54 teams competing in this years Student Robotics competition, situated from across the United Kingdom and Germany.
